      "text": "控えめに言って、最高のステージだったと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking modestly‚ I think that was a perfect performance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。会場のみんなが\nお星様みたいに、キラキラ輝いてた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Everyone in the audience\nwas sparkling‚ just like the stars.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.13281412594246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
