      "text": "何、泣いているんですの？\n結果発表はまだですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you crying?\nThey have yet to announce the results.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.03281412594246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
